{"tid":1984151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"職工盟繼續申請五一遊行","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T10:48:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c725238e36d5a7432997d7d1752a52121c48103c","tid":1984151,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/OD9FGeT.jpg\" /><br />\n【五一．社交距離遊行申請中】<br />\n今日有新聞話警察會反對由五一到七一嘅遊行集會，六四都打算唔畀搞。禁聚令一直延長下去，唔通香港人真係唔可以遊行？<br />\n<br />\n職工盟手足一早已經入紙申請五一遊行，因應疫情，我哋已議提出方案，以「四人一隊、保持社交距離」嘅方式舉行遊行。依個方法既附合禁聚令嘅要求，亦都無違反公安條例。警察係無理由反對嘅！<br />\n<br />\n政府唔封關，搞到經濟肅條。防疫基金拎成千億出嚟，但係普羅大眾就無受惠。與此同時，中共直接干預香港立法會嘅運作，已經令香港人忍無可忍。好多人都等緊一場遊行去表達意見，警察唔好再阻住曬！<br />\n<br />\n我哋會繼續向大家更新進度，五一我哋點都會有搞作！<br />\n<br />\n工會戰線 抗爭之路<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n#四人一隊<br />\n#保持社交距離<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/unionsforHK/907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FunionsforHK%2F907&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=47aafa7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/unionsforHK/907</a>"},{"pid":"3ffdc50d02a14be89be2071f88fb2cdd123e9472","tid":1984151,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8731a6ed14f3caa870c8ad0f8c4a086b7af277","tid":1984151,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81065394212cc2d3482aff2ddc10dcf2d7b6796c","tid":1984151,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c95